<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Christine & Kelly — A Proposal by Igor Demba Photography</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
 
  :root {
    --ivory:       #F7F4EE;
    --ivory-deep:  #EDE8DC;
    --parchment:   #E0D9C8;
    --ink:         #1C1C1A;
    --ink-soft:    #2E2C28;
    --warm-gray:   #6B6760;
    --taupe:       #9C9488;
    --accent:      #8C7355;
    --accent-lt:   #B09878;
    --border:      rgba(140,115,85,0.2);
    --border-soft: rgba(28,28,26,0.09);
    --white:       #FDFCFA;
  }
 
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
 
  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--ink);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
 
  /* ── IMAGES: force load regardless of referrer ── */
  img {
    referrerpolicy: no-referrer;
  }
 
  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 700px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--ink);
  }
 
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 45%;
    opacity: 0.88;
    transform: scale(1.04);
    transition: transform 10s ease;
  }
 
  .hero:hover .hero-bg { transform: scale(1.0); }
 
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      170deg,
      rgba(28,28,26,0.45) 0%,
      rgba(28,28,26,0.25) 30%,
      rgba(28,28,26,0.78) 75%,
      rgba(28,28,26,0.94) 100%
    );
  }
 
  .hero-content {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    padding: 0 24px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  }
 
  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.48em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(176,152,120,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp .8s ease forwards .2s;
  }
 
  .hero-names {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 14vw, 148px);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--ivory);
    line-height: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1.1s ease forwards .35s;
  }
 
  .hero-ampersand {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent-lt);
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards .5s;
  }
 
  .hero-ornament {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 28px 0 24px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp .8s ease forwards .7s;
  }
 
  .orn-line   { width: 64px; height: 1px; background: rgba(176,152,120,0.45); }
  .orn-diamond { width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--accent-lt); transform: rotate(45deg); flex-shrink: 0; }
 
  .hero-venue {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2.5vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.78);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp .9s ease forwards .85s;
  }
 
  .hero-meta {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.38);
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp .8s ease forwards 1s;
  }
 
  .hero-byline {
    margin-top: 44px;
    font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(176,152,120,0.5);
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp .8s ease forwards 1.15s;
  }
 
  /* ── OPENING NOTE ── */
  .opening {
    background: var(--ivory-deep);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
 
  .opening-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
 
  .opening-label {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.44em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 24px; display: block;
  }
 
  .opening-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(19px, 2.8vw, 27px);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-soft); letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .opening-sign {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe);
  }
 
  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }
  .section   { padding: 96px 0; }
 
  .section-label {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.44em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 18px; display: block;
  }
 
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 50px);
    font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
 
  .body-text {
    font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.95; color: var(--warm-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .rule { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
 
  /* ── SPLIT: text + image ── */
  .split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
 
  .split.rev { direction: rtl; }
  .split.rev > * { direction: ltr; }
 
  .split-img {
    overflow: hidden; min-height: 500px;
    background: var(--parchment);
    position: relative;
  }
 
  .split-img img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; display: block;
    transition: transform 7s ease;
  }
 
  .split-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
 
  .split-text {
    background: var(--ivory);
    padding: 80px 60px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  }
 
  /* ── VISION CARDS ── */
  .vision-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft); margin-top: 52px;
  }
 
  .vision-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 38px 28px;
    transition: background .25s;
  }
 
  .vision-card:hover { background: var(--ivory); }
 
  .vision-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--parchment); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
 
  .vision-title {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 11px;
  }
 
  .vision-desc {
    font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.85; color: var(--warm-gray);
  }
 
  /* ── GALLERY STRIP ── */
  .gallery-strip {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
    height: 400px;
  }
 
  .gal-item {
    overflow: hidden; position: relative;
    background: var(--parchment);
  }
 
  .gal-item img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; display: block;
    transition: transform 5s ease;
  }
 
  .gal-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.06); }
 
  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline {
    margin-top: 52px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
 
  .tl-day {
    padding: 44px 0 44px 52px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    position: relative;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    gap: 40px; align-items: start;
  }
 
  .tl-day::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 52px;
    width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  }
 
  .tl-day-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent); line-height: 1.2;
  }
 
  .tl-day-sub {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe); margin-top: 4px;
  }
 
  .tl-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
 
  .tl-item-title {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
 
  .tl-item-desc {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8; color: var(--warm-gray);
  }
 
  .tl-item { padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
  .tl-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
 
  /* ── PACKAGES ── */
  .packages-wrap {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px; margin-top: 52px;
  }
 
  .pkg {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    background: var(--white);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color .25s;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
 
  .pkg:hover { border-color: var(--border); }
 
  .pkg.featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--ink);
  }
 
  .pkg-head {
    padding: 44px 40px 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-head { border-bottom-color: rgba(140,115,85,0.2); }
 
  .pkg-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--accent); color: var(--ivory);
    padding: 5px 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
 
  .pkg-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 30px; font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-name { color: var(--ivory); }
 
  .pkg-tagline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--warm-gray); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-tagline { color: rgba(247,244,238,0.55); }
 
  .pkg-price {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 60px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1; color: var(--accent);
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-price { color: rgba(232,224,207,0.9); }
 
  .pkg-price sup { font-size: 24px; vertical-align: super; }
 
  .pkg-price-note {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--taupe); letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-price-note { color: rgba(156,148,136,0.6); }
 
  .pkg-body {
    padding: 36px 40px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
 
  .pkg-section-title {
    font-size: 8.5px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-section-title { color: var(--accent-lt); }
 
  .pkg-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
 
  .pkg-features li {
    font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--warm-gray);
    padding-left: 18px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5;
  }
 
  .pkg.featured .pkg-features li { color: rgba(247,244,238,0.58); }
 
  .pkg-features li::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 9px;
    width: 7px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent);
  }
 
  /* ── INVESTMENT TABLE ── */
  .inv-table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 44px;
  }
 
  .inv-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
 
  .inv-table td {
    padding: 18px 0; font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--warm-gray); font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
 
  .inv-table td:last-child {
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px; color: var(--ink);
  }
 
  .inv-total td {
    border-bottom: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-top: 24px;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    font-size: 12px !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
 
  .inv-total td:last-child {
    font-size: 40px !important;
    color: var(--accent) !important;
  }
 
  /* ── PROCESS STEPS ── */
  .process-steps {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5,1fr);
    gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    margin-top: 52px;
  }
 
  .proc-step {
    padding: 36px 26px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    position: relative;
  }
 
  .proc-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
 
  .proc-step::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 26px; right: 26px;
    height: 2px; background: var(--accent);
  }
 
  .proc-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 38px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--parchment); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
 
  .proc-title {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 9px;
  }
 
  .proc-desc {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8; color: var(--warm-gray);
  }
 
  /* ── QUOTE ── */
  .quote-band {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;
  }
 
  .qb-mark {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 72px; line-height: .5;
    color: rgba(140,115,85,0.3);
    display: block; margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
 
  .qb-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(19px, 2.8vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 300; color: rgba(247,244,238,0.82);
    line-height: 1.65; max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .qb-attr {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-lt);
  }
 
  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta-section {
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 560px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px;
  }
 
  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url('https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6164971a9996bd558e740f70/44725302-606e-4261-98db-7fbaec110305/IDP004.jpeg?format=2500w');
    background-size: cover; background-position: center top;
  }
 
  .cta-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(247,244,238,0.91);
  }
 
  .cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 560px; }
 
  .cta-label {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.44em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;
  }
 
  .cta-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
 
  .cta-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
 
  .cta-text {
    font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--warm-gray); line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .cta-email {
    display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
 
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex; gap: 14px;
    justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
 
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block; padding: 15px 48px;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--ivory);
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background .3s, transform .2s;
  }
 
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-1px); }
 
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block; padding: 15px 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink); color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all .3s;
  }
 
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--ivory); transform: translateY(-1px); }
 
  /* ── CREDENTIALS ── */
  .creds-strip {
    background: var(--ivory-deep);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    padding: 52px 40px;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: center; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
 
  .cred-name {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe);
  }
 
  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink); padding: 56px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(140,115,85,.18);
  }
 
  .footer-ck {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.35); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
 
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.38em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ivory); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
 
  .footer-sub {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(156,148,136,.55); margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
 
  .footer-links {
    display: flex; gap: 28px;
    justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
 
  .footer-links a {
    font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(156,148,136,.55);
    text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s;
  }
 
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent-lt); }
 
  /* ── ANIMATION ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
 
  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .split, .split.rev { grid-template-columns: 1fr; direction: ltr; }
    .split-img { min-height: 360px; }
    .split-text { padding: 52px 28px; }
    .vision-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
    .gallery-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); height: auto; }
    .gal-item { height: 220px; }
    .packages-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tl-day { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; padding-left: 36px; }
    .process-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .proc-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
    .proc-step::before { top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; width: 100%; }
    .container { padding: 0 20px; }
    .creds-strip { gap: 24px; padding: 40px 20px; }
  }
 
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .vision-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .gallery-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
 
<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-intro">A Photography Proposal for</div>
 
    <div class="hero-names">Christine</div>
    <div class="hero-ampersand">&amp;</div>
    <div class="hero-names" style="animation-delay: .45s;">Kelly</div>
 
    <div class="hero-ornament">
      <div class="orn-line"></div>
      <div class="orn-diamond"></div>
      <div class="orn-line"></div>
    </div>
 
    <p class="hero-venue">Brush Creek Ranch · Wyoming</p>
    <p class="hero-meta"> Three-Day Celebration</p>
    <p class="hero-byline">Photography by Igor Demba</p>
  </div>
</header>
 
<!-- ── OPENING NOTE ── -->
<div class="opening">
  <div class="opening-inner">
    <span class="opening-label">A Personal Note</span>
    <p class="opening-text">"Christine — from the moment you described your vision, I knew exactly what kind of images we would make together. An unconventional love story, a cowboy chapel in Wyoming, two families becoming one. This is the work I live for. I'm honoured to be on your shortlist, and I hope this proposal shows you exactly how I intend to tell your story."</p>
    <p class="opening-sign">— Igor Demba</p>
  </div>
